  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\">What is the slope of the graph of <math alttext=\"y equals one third left parenthesis 29 x plus 10 right parenthesis plus 5 x\"><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>3</mn></mfrac><mfenced><mrow><mn>29</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>10</mn></mrow></mfenced><mo>+</mo><mn>5</mn><mi>x</mi></math>&nbsp;in the&nbsp;<em>xy</em>-plane?</p>",
